snippet.title: Don't Die in the West Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist Don't Die in the West on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1751350/Dont_Die_In_The_West/
Join our Discord: https://discord.gg/7rYwpXTEZJ
Follow Don't Die in the West on Twitter: https://twitter.com/DDInTheWest

Don’t Die in the West is an open-world cowboy-life RPG for 1-4 players. Start a new life on the prairie, explore the frontier, and build a ranch of your own. As you avenge the untimely demise of your uncle, will you become a heroic cowboy or a notorious outlaw?
